Description:
Along the way you meet two beggar elves, a man and a woman, both ragged and hungry.

They tell you that when the Frost Calamity descended from the skies freezing the city, they weren't there and they were lucky. But that ruined their way of life and it is impossible for them to return to the city to retrieve their belongings.

They want to flee Faeborg, but they had to sell what little they had to eat and the prices to get on a ship are expensive.
DescriptionAction: Each of them asks you for money separately.
